<h2 class="wsite-content-title"><font color="#008621" size="5">Our Vision</font></h2>

<div class="paragraph">Our vision is to see people feeling less stressed about their medical transportations needs and being free to fully perform their daily activities even in wheelchairs or Stretchers.</div>

<h2 class="wsite-content-title"><font color="#008621" size="5">Why We Were Founded</font></h2>

<div class="paragraph">We were first created for kids transportation. Because we have noticed many parents don't really need a Nanny. All they need is a reliable, responsible, affordable and punctual transportation that has high safety rules in place to commute their children to/from School, Camps, Daycare, Training section on the field etc. However, there were very few affordable Kids' Transportation Companies in the Washington DC area. Therefore, we went ahead and created one, whose conciliate safety, responsibility, comfort, and affordability to solve our area's parents difficulties.<br />However, on our way, we&nbsp;discovered that there were more unfulfilled demands with medical transportation needs. Specially, those who were on beds&#128716; or in wheelchair &#9855; and sometimes with no elevators, were the most left behind. So our boarding direction decided to get specialized in non-emergency medical transportation, where was the most needs.&nbsp;</div>

