<h2 class="wsite-content-title"><font color="#008621" size="5">Flexibility</font></h2>

<div class="paragraph">Our team of field service representatives (FSRs) provide full transportation services to patients and the elderly to the tune of 200+ rides each day for many organizations. It is because of our excellent staff that we can provide timely, reliable transportation to accommodate non-traditional trips requests and meet the needs of your clients and patients. Our flexibility makes it exponentially easier to arrange prompt and safe transportation for our precious Clients. From <a href="http://rideemt.com/services/wheelchair-transportation-services/">Ambulatory to Wheelchair</a>,&nbsp;<strong style="color:rgb(98, 98, 98)"><u>or</u></strong>&nbsp; <u><strong>Stairs'</strong></u><strong><u><u>&nbsp;</u>Chair</u></strong>,&nbsp;<strong style="color:rgb(98, 98, 98)"><u>or</u></strong>&nbsp;<a href="http://rideemt.com/services/medical-van-transportation/">Stretcher</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="http://rideemt.com/services/dialysis-transportation-services/">BLS</a>&nbsp;rides for family members, we have the capabilities to provide the most convenient ride for all non-emergency situations.</div>

<h2 class="wsite-content-title"><font color="#008621" size="5">Partnerships</font></h2>

